description: Cute Studio on East 73rd street in heart of the Upper East Side, one block from the new 2nd ave / Q subway. Apartment is bright  and fully furnished. It has full kitchen, Full size bed, with comfy mattress and clean bathroom. Apple TV, Wifi,linens, towels, toiletries provided. Only 7 min to Times sq , only 6 blocks walk to central park and museum mile (Guggenheim, Met-Breuer) We offer Early check in and also Late check out!
name: Brand New Cute & Cozy Studio, East 73rd!!
review: If you are looking for a place to crash in the evenings, this is it. It has everything you need and nothing you don't. It's close to the subway, so you can get everywhere while staying out of the hustle and bustle.
